      "start": 402.81,
      "end": 403.25,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 403.35,
      "end": 403.71,
      "text": "Mature."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.01,
      "end": 406.17,
      "text": "How do you say that in the British way?"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.17,
      "end": 407.89,
      "text": "저한테 지금 질문하시는 거예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.91,
      "end": 408.25,
      "text": "Mature."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.87,
      "end": 409.99,
      "text": "저 앞에 있으니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.53,
      "end": 411.23,
      "text": "우리 놀아밖에."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.35,
      "end": 411.83,
      "text": "아유."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.85,
      "end": 412.49,
      "text": "놀아 뿐이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.63,
      "end": 412.97,
      "text": "아니에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 413.33,
      "end": 414.23,
      "text": "미국식으로 할게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.67,
      "end": 415.23,
      "text": "Mature."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.49,
      "end": 416.03,
      "text": "이거 맞나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.11,
      "end": 417.27,
      "text": "That sounded more British."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.45,
      "end": 418.11,
      "text": "아, 진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.11,
      "end": 418.47,
      "text": "Mature."
    },
    {
      "start": 418.59,
      "end": 419.15,
      "text": "We say mature."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.47,
      "end": 422.35,
      "text": "아, 오늘 컨디션이 너무 British drogue로 갔네."
    },
    {
      "start": 422.99,
      "end": 424.93,
      "text": "어떤 내용인지 너무너무 궁금해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.79,
      "end": 426.67,
      "text": "Okay, it's an interview."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.87,
      "end": 427.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 427.15,
      "end": 432.07,
      "text": "There's a panel of men interviewing this one young lady."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.27,
      "end": 432.61,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.61,
      "end": 436.07,
      "text": "And she's very nervous, but she holds her own."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.17,
      "end": 436.45,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.49,
      "end": 437.37,
      "text": "She's doing a good job."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.49,
      "end": 438.53,
      "text": "얼마나 떨렸을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.81,
      "end": 442.35,
      "text": "Studying here is a big commitment."
    },
    {
      "start": 442.75,
      "end": 442.91,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.63,
      "end": 446.05,
      "text": "Davidson 교수가 하는 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.17,
      "end": 448.59,
      "text": "Studying here is a big commitment."
    },
    {
      "start": 449.77,
      "end": 454.33,
      "text": "Studying here, 여기에서 공부하는 것은, is a big commitment."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.57,
      "end": 455.11,
      "text": "무슨 의미예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.11,
      "end": 458.55,
      "text": "아주 큰 전념이 필요하다라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 458.63,
      "end": 466.35,
      "text": "You need a lot of time and effort and dedication to study at our prestigious university."
    },
    {
      "start": 466.61,
      "end": 470.41,
      "text": "만만하게 생각하면 안 되고, 아주 중요한 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.77,
      "end": 474.15,
      "text": "아주 큰 전념과 약속과 헌신이 필요합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.35,
      "end": 476.39,
      "text": "공부라는 게 여기에서는 이라는 의미예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.39,
      "end": 482.25,
      "text": "He just found out that she has a child to take care of, so they're worried that she won't"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.25,
      "end": 484.89,
      "text": "have enough time to dedicate to her studies."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.07,
      "end": 485.27,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 486.73,
      "end": 487.15,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.59,
      "end": 491.23,
      "text": "I managed my diploma whilst looking after my daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.71,
      "end": 492.31,
      "text": "Oh, whilst?"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.71,
      "end": 493.67,
      "text": "Oh, whilst?"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.67,
      "end": 493.99,
      "text": "고급."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.35,
      "end": 495.57,
      "text": "아, 이거 고급이에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.93,
      "end": 496.23,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.63,
      "end": 498.31,
      "text": "Americans never say that."
    },
    {
      "start": 498.45,
      "end": 500.47,
      "text": "It's kind of old style English."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.67,
      "end": 501.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.15,
      "end": 503.63,
      "text": "I know this word is considered archaic."
    },
    {
      "start": 503.93,
      "end": 504.45,
      "text": "Archaic."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.59,
      "end": 504.87,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 505.07,
      "end": 506.43,
      "text": "Yes, it's a bit archaic."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.61,
      "end": 506.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.25,
      "end": 512.19,
      "text": "미국식 영어에서는 조금 고대 영어 정도로 받아들이는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.37,
      "end": 514.91,
      "text": "And maybe, I don't know if they still use it that much."
