    {
      "start": 564.89,
      "end": 565.25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.59,
      "end": 566.59,
      "text": "Yeah, she graduated."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.79,
      "end": 568.79,
      "text": "So, 졸업은 한 것 같아요."
